698
00:36:26,080 --> 00:36:27,680
Is it Tom or is it Kavlarananin

699
00:36:27,680 --> 00:36:29,600
that doesn't remember the locked cabinet

700
00:36:29,600 --> 00:36:30,480
in Nina's office?

701
00:36:30,480 --> 00:36:32,400
Oh, I did not remember it at all.

702
00:36:33,200 --> 00:36:34,800
Now that you mentioned it, I remember it,

703
00:36:34,800 --> 00:36:36,400
but it was not coming to me.

704
00:36:36,400 --> 00:36:37,200
Yeah, fair enough.

705
00:36:39,200 --> 00:36:39,920
No, absolutely.

706
00:36:39,920 --> 00:36:41,200
I remember spying it and everything.

707
00:36:42,320 --> 00:36:44,639
How do I get Tom to break into this office

708
00:36:44,639 --> 00:36:46,800
without saying Tom break into this office?

709
00:36:47,680 --> 00:36:50,000
This season seems like it's just going to end in crime.

710
00:36:50,000 --> 00:36:50,800
All around crime.

711
00:36:50,800 --> 00:36:52,079
Yeah, it's ending in crime 100%.

712
00:36:52,079 --> 00:36:54,240
Everyone's going to do a crime.

713
00:36:54,240 --> 00:36:58,160
Except Alydin, who's been doing crime to survive.

714
00:37:00,000 --> 00:37:01,840
The fact that I'm not doing crime right now,

715
00:37:01,840 --> 00:37:04,400
I'm on the up and up getting paid and then crying shit.

716
00:37:07,200 --> 00:37:10,400
Amy not doing crime is almost a crime in and of itself.

717
00:37:10,400 --> 00:37:11,039
Agreed.

718
00:37:11,039 --> 00:37:12,000
I know, right?

719
00:37:12,000 --> 00:37:13,039
When am I the good one?

